Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
writeVSMappingFile(25.10)                            writeVSMappingFile(25.10)

Name
       writeVSMappingFile  -  Writes out a bump mapping file for Voltage Storm
       use

Syntax
       writeVSMappingFile

       <fileName>

       Writes out a bump mapping file for Voltage Storm use. Use this  command
       after  the aligned power bump pairs are created by the readBumpLocation
       command.

Parameters
       <fileName>
              Specifies the file name.

Examples
              * The following command creates a power bump mapping file:

                writeVSMappingFile powerBump.mapping

Related Information
              * readBumpLocation

